胸片检查确诊为“小儿肺炎”入院。为防止并发症的发生，护士应重点观察患儿的","discription":"","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswj_ay_0908_20154","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"心率、呼吸变化","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"大小便次数","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"体温变化","fourth":"精神状况","answerPic":"","first":"饮水量"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患儿，8个月，弛张性高热1天。患儿精神萎靡、呻吟，呼吸困难。查体：双肺下方有固定的中细湿哕音，皮肤散在猩红热样疹。X线胸片：示双肺下有大片阴影，病灶中心呈蜂窝状。诊断金黄色葡萄球菌肺炎。其抗生素使用应至体温正常后","discription":"小儿支气管肺炎抗生素的用药时间一般持续到体温正常后5～7天，临床症状消失后3天。支原体肺炎首选大环内酯类抗生素，至少用药2～3周；金黄色葡萄球菌肺炎在体温正常后2～3周停药，总疗程≥6周。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswj_ay_0909_20154","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"E","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"3～5天","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"5～7天","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"14～21天","fourth":"7～14天","answerPic":"","first":"2～3天"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患儿，3岁，支气管肺炎入院。医嘱需要给患儿输液，护士执行该医嘱时，滴速应控制在每小时","discription":"减慢输液速度以预防心力衰竭，输液时滴速应控制在每小时5ml／kg。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswj_ay_0910_20154","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"12ml／kg","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"15ml／kg","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"30m1／kg","fourth":"25m1／kg","answerPic":"","first":"5ml/kg"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"支气管扩张患者痰液的特点是","discription":"大量脓痰，静置后可分3层：上层为泡沫、中层为黏液、下层为脓性物和坏死组织，伴有厌氧菌感染时痰液恶臭。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswj_ay_0911_20154","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"大量脓痰久置分3层","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"铁锈色","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"粉红色泡沫痰","fourth":"暗